<!-- +++++++++++ Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Pre_defined_datum_3d_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol">
<p>
A <b>Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:arm:Non_feature_shape_element_arm.Non_feature_shape_definition"/> and a type of <express_ref linkend="Layered_3d_shape:arm:Layered_3d_shape_arm.three_dimensional_shape"/>.  A <b>Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol</b> is a standard representation for a <express_ref linkend="Extended_geometric_tolerance:arm:Extended_geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum_axis"/> in a 3 dimensional coordinate system.
</p></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Pre_defined_datum_3d_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol.associated_element">
the <b>associated_element</b> specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Extended_geometric_tolerance:arm:Extended_geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum_axis"/> for the <b>Pre_defined_datum_axis_3d_symbol</b>.
</ext_description>
<!-- +++++++++++ Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Pre_defined_datum_3d_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol">
<p>
A <b>Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:arm:Non_feature_shape_element_arm.Non_feature_shape_definition"/> and a type of  <express_ref linkend="Layered_3d_shape:arm:Layered_3d_shape_arm.three_dimensional_shape"/>.  A <b>Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol</b> is a standard representation for a <express_ref linkend="Extended_geometric_tolerance:arm:Extended_geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum_plane"/> in a 3 dimensional coordinate system.  A <b>Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol</b> shall be parallel with the normal vector of the plane, and shall intersect the plane at the origin of the symbol.
</p></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Pre_defined_datum_3d_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol.associated_element">
the <b>associated_element</b> specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Extended_geometric_tolerance:arm:Extended_geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum_plane"/> for the <b>Pre_defined_datum_plane_3d_symbol</b>.
</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>

